issue.title: Can no longer play back tunnel circuit logs in current docker image

content.raw:
it could be due to the difference between model versions, e.g.  if the log is recorded using version 3 of the ModelX and the new docker image has version 4 downloaded in the cache, the playback would fail.

If you run into this problem again, could you paste the errors / warnings from the console?
